So my school has this competition in the summer where we make teams and basically do stupid shit for points (I'm talking, slightly illegal, mostly sexual or at the very least, rude shit). About halfway through when the entire operation almost got busted by janitors, my friends realized how much it sucked and we bailed to smoke and drink in the park. It was fun. 

I don't smoke, but seeing my friend flailing on a side and screaming about how much she hated the republican party was fun.
